      <title>印度财政部长呼吁降低利率，因印度储备银行维持通胀目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/india-finance-minister-says-bank-rates-should-be-more-affordable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于亚洲第三大经济体增长放缓的担忧正浮现在政策制定者的公开言论中，政府推动降低利率，而央行则坚持首先实现通胀目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/india-finance-minister-says-bank-rates-should-be-more-affordable</guid>
